section that we're all seeing the worst in
people. I will say that some of the [INAUDIBLE]

00:13:57.600 --> 00:14:03.059
Urban Baby? I've never, I've never gone onto
the discussion board but my husband did after

00:14:03.059 --> 00:14:07.339
he, someone called and said there's some emails
you really need to take a look at this, he

00:14:07.339 --> 00:14:11.980
goes in his office, he comes out after an
hour. He's like pale and shaking and he gets

