of them were laced with this unbelievable

00:15:35.139 --> 00:15:40.759
venom, this loathing for everything about
me, and I just couldn't stand to read them

00:15:40.759 --> 00:15:48.709
anymore. For somebody who writes with so much
narcissistic self-absorption, I am very thin-skinned

00:15:48.709 --> 00:15:52.730
and I respond to almost all criticism, at
least personal criticism, by falling into

00:15:52.730 --> 00:15:57.260
a pit of self-loathing where I'm convinced
that the person doing the criticizing is absolutely

00:15:57.260 --> 00:16:04.499
right, and I am as awful as she, and it's
