00:17:02.629 --> 00:17:06.800
he's going to go into the shower and beat
off because he's so excited about me [laughter]

00:17:06.800 --> 00:17:12.329
maybe not. Um, but you know look, just even
reading those now, as I'm doing it as a joke,

00:17:12.329 --> 00:17:17.510
but I'm still gives me this, kind of like
ah, in my stomach and I think really, really

